43:52.680 --> 43:55.147
Well, it's just that
I love this country.

43:55.838 --> 43:58.938
I love the glory of
Fort Sumter and Bull Run.

43:59.256 --> 44:00.256
I never in my...

44:01.015 --> 44:03.215
