47:08.498 --> 47:10.464
Now, you mothers get your
knees out of each other's groins

47:10.589 --> 47:11.921
and your teeth out
of each other's butts

47:12.756 --> 47:13.756
and do what I tell ya!

47:14.431 --> 47:15.431
