49:45.154 --> 49:46.287
Who informed ya?

49:46.299 --> 49:49.099
Well, let's just say I've been
informed and leave it at that.

49:49.672 --> 49:52.172
No, just tell me who informed
ya and leave it at that.

49:52.823 --> 49:54.790
Are you late for
class or aren'tcha?

49:55.259 --> 49:59.925
