Playboy by next week.

51:40.034 --> 51:42.134
And I sure hope it got
more to it than this.

51:43.358 --> 51:44.358
It has.

51:46.507 --> 51:49.807
- What you doin' here, Conrack?
- Fishin'.

51:50.177 --> 51:52.844
