doin' here on this island?

51:53.323 --> 51:54.923
You the only white man here.

51:55.118 --> 51:57.618
I mean, except for Ryder,
he's only here 'cause his store is.

52:00.486 --> 52:01.486
Well, I'll tell ya.

52:04.662 --> 52:05.662
