52:22.758 --> 52:24.958
Now I'm just teachin' school.

52:28.494 --> 52:29.494
Ugh!

52:30.867 --> 52:31.867
Mercy.

52:32.466 --> 52:35.266
- You ever been off this island?
- No.

52:36.906 --> 52:37.939
You ever wanna get off it?

52:39.632 --> 52:40.632
Nh-nh.

52:41.827 --> 52:43.227
