You dirty son of a bitch!

54:42.254 --> 54:43.254
No profanity!

54:45.719 --> 54:46.852
Just proficiency.

54:47.450 --> 54:48.450
All right.

54:49.925 --> 54:50.925
Keep tryin'.

54:51.251 --> 54:53.051
Let's go. C'mon, everybody in!

54:53.485 --> 54:54.818
You can stand there.

54:56.225 --> 54:57.725
Okay. C'mon.
Come on in the water.

54:58.876 --> 55:01.209
Ronnie, come here.
Stay in that water.

55:02.321 --> 55:03.988
Mary, stay in that water.
C'mere.

