55:37.579 --> 55:39.245
Another cup of water. See?

55:45.954 --> 55:47.387
Yeah, that's good, pal.

55:53.604 --> 55:55.071
Kick your feet! C'mon!

55:56.690 --> 55:57.690
Attaboy, Mac.

